"title": "2218: Jesus Christ, Son of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2218: jesus christ, son of god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A title emphasising Jesus Christ's deity, his office as Messiah and his pre-eminence as the object of the church's faith and worship and as the content of its gospel.</p>\n<h2>``Son of God'' in the OT</h2>\n<h3>Israel as God's son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:22-Exod4:23\">EXO 4:22–4:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:9\">JER 31:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:20\">JER 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a></p>\n<h3>The future Messiah/king as God's Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:7\">PSA 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:27\">PSA 89:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:33\">ACT 13:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:5\">HEB 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:5\">HEB 5:5</a> <em>Jesus Christ perfectly fulfils all the OT promises concerning God's son, whether referring originally to Israel or to the Messiah.</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the Son of God</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ affirms he is God's Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:36\">JHN 10:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:70\">LUK 22:70</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:63-Matt26:64\">MAT 26:63–26:64</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61-Mark14:62\">MRK 14:61–14:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:7\">JHN 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:18\">REV 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>The Father affirms Jesus Christ is his Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Others affirm Jesus Christ is God's Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:33\">MAT 14:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:39\">MRK 15:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:54\">MAT 27:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:34\">JHN 1:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:14\">HEB 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:3\">2JN 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Demons affirm Jesus Christ is God's Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:7\">MRK 5:7</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:29\">MAT 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:28\">LUK 8:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:11\">MRK 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:41\">LUK 4:41</a></p>\n<h2>``Son of God'' as a taunt</h2>\n<p>By the devil in the wilderness:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:3\">MAT 4:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:3\">LUK 4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:6\">MAT 4:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:9\">LUK 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:40\">MAT 27:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:43\">MAT 27:43</a></p>\n<h2>``Son of God'' stresses Jesus Christ's deity</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the Son of God the Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:35\">JHN 3:35</a></strong> <em>In John's Gospel in particular, the terms Son/Father are used many times to speak of Jesus Christ's unique relationship with God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:22\">LUK 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36\">MAT 24:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:20-John5:22\">JHN 5:20–5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:3\">1JN 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:22-1John2:23\">1JN 2:22–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:9\">2JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>``Son of God'' implies Jesus Christ's equality with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:18\">JHN 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:23\">JHN 5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:30\">JHN 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:33\">JHN 10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9-John14:10\">JHN 14:9–14:10</a></p>\n<h2>``Son of God'' implies Jesus Christ's obedience to the Father</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:19\">JHN 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:42\">MAT 26:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28\">JHN 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49\">JHN 12:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:31\">JHN 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:19\">ROM 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">HEB 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:9\">HEB 10:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as ``Son of God'' is the Messiah</h2>\n<h3>``Son of God'' as a Messianic title for Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:63-Matt26:64\">MAT 26:63–26:64</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61-Mark14:62\">MRK 14:61–14:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:70-Luke23:2\">LUK 22:70–23:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16\">MAT 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:1\">MRK 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32\">LUK 1:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:41\">LUK 4:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:27\">JHN 11:27</a></p>\n<h3>``Son of God'' as one sent by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4\">GAL 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:37\">MAT 21:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:6\">MRK 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:13\">LUK 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:17\">JHN 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3\">ROM 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:32\">ROM 8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9\">1JN 4:9</a></p>\n<h2>Grounds for regarding Jesus Christ as the Son of God</h2>\n<h3>The virgin birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:3-Rom1:4\">ROM 1:3–1:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:36-John10:38\">JHN 10:36–10:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:17\">JHN 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:19\">JHN 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:36\">JHN 5:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:11\">JHN 14:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's oneness with the Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:30\">JHN 10:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:45\">JHN 12:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10\">JHN 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21\">JHN 17:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as Son of God is the object of the church's faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:37\">ACT 8:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:23\">1JN 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:15\">1JN 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:5\">1JN 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:13\">1JN 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as Son of God is the content of the church's gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:9\">ROM 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:20\">ACT 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:19\">2CO 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:9-1John5:12\">1JN 5:9–5:12</a></p>",
